{
  "bookId": "laozi-boshu",
  "num": 21,
  "title": "第二十一章（從道）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "孔德之容 唯道是從 道之物 唯朢唯忽"
    },
    {
      "text": "忽呵望呵 中有象呵 朢呵忽呵 中有物呵 幽呵鳴呵 中有請呵 亓請甚真 亓中有信"
    },
    {
      "text": "自今及古 亓名不去 以順眾父"
    },
    {
      "text": "吾何以知眾父之祭 以此"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 5,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "唯，獨也。大德之人，不隨世俗所行，獨從於道也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 18
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "道之於萬物，獨怳忽往來，於其無所定也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 18
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "道唯忽怳無形，之中獨有萬物法象。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 18
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "道唯怳忽，其中有一，經營生化，因氣立質。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 18
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "道唯窈冥無形，其中有精實，神明相薄，陰陽交會也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 18
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言存精氣，其妙甚真，非有飾也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 35,
          "end": 36
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "道匿功藏名，其信在中也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 39
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "自，從也。自古至今，道常在不去。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 39
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "閱，稟也。甫，始也。言道稟與，萬物始生，從道受氣。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 39
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "吾何以知萬物從道受氣。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 9,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "此，今也。以今萬物皆得道精氣而生，動作起居，非道不然。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ],
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 18
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "孔，空也，惟以空為德，然後乃能動作從道。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 18
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "恍惚，無形不繫之歎。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 18
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以無形始物，不繫成物，萬物以始以成，而不知其所以然，故曰，恍兮惚兮、惚兮恍兮，其中有象也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 18
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "窈、冥，深遠之歎，深遠不可得而見。然而萬物由之，其可得見，以定其真。故曰，窈兮冥兮，其中有精也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 18
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "信，信驗也。物反窈冥，則真精之極得，萬物之性定。故曰，其精甚真，其中有信也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 1
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "至真之極，不可得名，無名則是其名也。自古及今，無不由此而成，故曰，自古及今，其名不去也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 14
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "眾甫，物之始也。以無名說萬物始也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "此上之所云也。言吾何以知萬物之始於無哉，以此知之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
